data.description: This exquisite home boasts 20 ft volume ceilings offering natural lighting, spacious & open ambiance designed for entertainment, with distinct formal living & family room spaces that accommodate both intimate gatherings & larger social events. Unique features include 100 sq ft loft upstairs, eat-in kitchen with granite countertops, travertine backsplash, & 42 inch cabinetry full of storage. The outdoors greets you with a perfect screened-in patio, resort style pool & expansive backyard large enough for all your entertaining during your events. Zone to A+ elementary school, 0.7 mi. from Chabad, 1.1 miles from Sawgrass trailhead where you can enjoy beautiful sunsets. Roof is 2006, all windows have storm protection & partial impact doors & windows, crown molding throughout, water heater 2018.
